      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 244.04,
      "start_time": 240.56,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 32,
      "text": "Um But thank you, thank you so much for taking the time to connect with me today."
    },
    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 251.94,
      "start_time": 244.05,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 33,
      "text": "Uh As far as my agenda goes, I wanted to learn a little bit about um where you're seeing apartment IQ working really well for you."
    },
    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 254.82,
      "start_time": 252.26,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 34,
      "text": "Um And what your plans are for 2024."
    },
    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 257.34,
      "start_time": 255.13,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 35,
      "text": "Um We'd love to keep the partnership going."
