    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 268.63,
      "start_time": 266.21,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 39,
      "text": "Anything you're thinking about on this call specifically?"
    },
    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 282.07,
      "start_time": 269.01,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 40,
      "text": "Well, I'd like to do you have like some metrics that you can provide me for that like apartment IQ to, to be honest, I mean, I, I don't necessarily know if I find it super valuable because I kind of know already like where we're in competition with."
    },
    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 287.38,
      "start_time": 282.55,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 41,
      "text": "So I'm not sure if we want to continue with that apartment IQ to be honest,"
    },
    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 307.66,
      "start_time": 288.45,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 42,
      "text": "I just don't think that like the cost that it, you know, the cost that it it is for us is really, you know, giving us information that we don't kind of already know um just with what the market is, you know, what, where we're at in relation to where others are."
    },
    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 311.77,
      "start_time": 307.69,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 43,
      "text": "Um So I, I don't necessarily know if, if we find that super helpful"
    },
    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 316.41,
      "start_time": 313.47,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 44,
      "text": "and of course, you know, your markets, it sounds like really."
    },
    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 316.93,
      "start_time": 316.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 45,
      "text": "Well."
    },
    {
      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 319.87,
      "start_time": 316.96,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 46,
      "text": "Um, tell me a little bit about those, those properties."
