      "end_time": 373.98,
      "start_time": 364.59,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 63,
      "text": "Um And if they did, it really doesn't matter to us because we don't really drive those concessions, you know, we just, we, we don't really believe in concessions."
