      "id": "fbd8c92c-2a71-4f81-9d23-6f521d3a9a98",
      "recording_id": "e7add522-8ea6-4e9d-9fd3-481a5cd4bbad",
      "end_time": 395.3,
      "start_time": 378.78,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 65,
      "text": "Um But it just, we don't offer concessions and, and, and I know that it's like, I don't really care if others do because if, if you're looking, if you have a person who's literally only looking for price point, regardless of the value, they're just going to go with whoever has, they're going to get, you know, free rent from."
