      "end_time": 403.59,
      "start_time": 395.85,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 66,
      "text": "And I don't necessarily know if we find that really fruitful because then they don't, they don't stay because they're just going to move on to the next, you know, free rent that they get."
